div.span: Welcome to the Towers of Hanoi!

div.style: text-align: left;
text-align: left;
div.span: Your goal is to move the shapes from the first rod to the last rod. The biggest shape needs to be at the bottom, the smallest shape on the top.

div.style: text-align: left;
text-align: left;
div.span: Rules:

div.style: text-align: left;
div.span: 1.Only one shape may be moved at a time.

div.style: text-align: left;
div.span: 2. Each move consists of taking the upper shape from one of the stacks and placing it on top of another stack or on an empty rod.

div.style: text-align: left;
div.span: 3. No shape may be placed on top of a disk that is smaller than itself.

div.style: text-align: left;
text-align: left;
div.span: How to play:

div.style: text-align: left;
div.span: 1. Indicate the stack from which you want to move the uppermost shape

div.style: text-align: left;
div.span: 2. Indicate the stack on which you want to place the uppermost weight.

div.style: text-align: left;
text-align: left;
div.span: Good luck!
